--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 1
Use case        : email template management
Scenario name   : add email template
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert values and press the button "Conferma".

Expected results:

1. The new email template is added to the system.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 2
Use case        : email template management
Scenario name   : modify email template
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert an emailtemplate as in scenario 1.
5. Select the link "Modifica" for the template jut inserted.

Expected results:

1. The email template is correctly changed.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 3
Use case        : email template management
Scenario name   : delete email template
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert an emailtemplate as in scenario 1.
5. Select the link "Cancella" and confirm the deletion.

Expected results:

1. The email template is correctly deleted.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 4
Use case        : email template management
Scenario name   : paging
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert 25 emailtemplate repeteaing 25 times scenario 1.
5. Verify the paging adding, removing end changing the templates.

Expected results:

1. The email template paging works fine.

